snippet: The Army Corps of Engineers will not meet a legal deadline for completing a plan to prevent Asian carp from invading the Great Lakes, Representative Dave Camp said Friday.
abstract: Rep Dave Camp says Army Corps of Engineers will not meet legal deadline for completing plan to prevent Asian carp from invading Great Lakes, and that he plans to hold corps accountable.
lead_paragraph: The Army Corps of Engineers will not meet a legal deadline for completing a plan to prevent Asian carp from invading the Great Lakes, Representative Dave Camp said Friday.

headline.main: Michigan: Plan on Carp Falters, Congressman Says
headline.print_headline: Michigan: Plan On Carp Falters, Congressman Says
